<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT-Serfin starts Cemex at buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT-Serfin starts Cemex at buy.</headline>
<text>
<p>--Grupo Financiero Serfin started coverage of Cemex with a buy recommendation.</p>
<p>--Analyst Gerardo Saenz predicts EPS of 4.06 pesos in 1996 and 2.47 pesos in 1997.</p>
<p>--Says Cemex prospects for 1997 look good on strength of debt restructuring.</p>
<p>--More direct foreign investment expected.</p>
<p>--Privatizations, government housing projects seen helping construction sector.</p>
<p>--Price increases in Caribbean and technological improvements also seen boosting share prices.</p>
<p>--Monterrey bureau, (528) 345-7677</p>
